  Check SESAM real variable types:
  ================================
  Precision kr :
  --------------
  kr              =           8
  digits(xprec)   =          53
  epsilon(xprec)  =  2.220446049250313E-016
  huge(xprec)     =  1.797693134862316E+308
  precision(xprec)=          15
  
  Precision kr8:
  --------------
  kr8              =           8
  digits(xprec8)   =          53
  epsilon(xprec8)  =  2.220446049250313E-016
  huge(xprec8)     =  1.797693134862316E+308
  precision(xprec8)=          15
  
  Precision kr4:
  --------------
  kr4              =           4
  digits(xprec4)   =          24
  epsilon(xprec4)  =  1.1920929E-07
  huge(xprec4)     =  3.4028235E+38
  precision(xprec4)=           6
 
 *** ROUTINE : sesam/defcst :
          define SESAM configuration
 *** sesam/defcst/defswi :
          define SESAM structure
 *** ROUTINE sesam/defcst/defctl :
          load user configuration
 *** ROUTINE : sesam/defctl/readlist :
          read SESAM configuration file
